<item>
            <title>[LU-284] lustre-module got dependency issue when installing RHEL6 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-284</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When installing the latest RHEL6 master build(#105), got following error message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some of the packages you have selected for install are&lt;br/&gt;
missing dependencies.  You can exit the installation,&lt;br/&gt;
go back and change your package selections, or continue&lt;br/&gt;
installing these packages without their dependencies. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre-modules-2.0.59-2.6.32_71.18.2.el6_lustre.g2428b0c.x86 &lt;br/&gt;
_64_gabb98b8.x86_64 requires kernel =                      &lt;br/&gt;
2.6.32-71.18.2.el6_lustre.g2428b0c.x86_64 &lt;/p&gt;</description>
